  "body": "<p>Studio Calico's <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/34th-street-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">34th Street December kit</a> is still available. Every month when I get the kits, I have a little routine that I go through. Here is how this layout came together using the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/34th-street-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">main kit only</a>. The firs thing I do is open up the main kit and spread everything out. I like to flip the papers to my favorite sides facing up so I can choose which ones to use.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d2e1ec3062b0d5ec.jpg?v=1782537996\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Then I gather my favorite tools, including the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/other-tools/brad-setter-and-piercing-tool?aff=6cc2c70f\">Brad Setter from We R Memory Keepers</a> and the BEST WHITE PEN ever made, aka <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/pens-markers/uni-ball-white-pen?aff=6cc2c70f\">Uniball Signo</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cf64b54e654a8045.jpg?v=1782537999\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I lay it all out, choose photos and begin the fun process of piecing it all together.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13c-41-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/53e3147efd2d5812.jpg?v=1782538002\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"13d-8-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f80ad07c32350984.jpg?v=1782538005\">\n</img>\n\n\n\n<p>I made some splatter with the mists that I wasn't too happy with. No big deal, because I just placed my photo right over it.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13e-9-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cdab96976cb6dad4.jpg?v=1782538007\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13f-9a-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/728e602ff3312838.jpg?v=1782538010\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13g-9b-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/63c64dd960d55180.jpg?v=1782538013\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13h-9c-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/157c35764095abb0.jpg?v=1782538015\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13i-9d-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e9dd8dd7bb87fcbc.jpg?v=1782538018\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13j-9e-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ba73a4b8e00730cf.jpg?v=1782538021\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13k-9f-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/15ef05244d61bff0.jpg?v=1782538024\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13l-9g-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/aa2c49c04f42c9f3.jpg?v=1782538027\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13m-DownUnderSC-449x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c0e1a9f18b4b2774.jpg?v=1782538029\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Hope you enjoyed seeing the layout come together. You can see all that I created with the December kits in <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/design-team-gallery/34th-street-scrapbook-kit/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">my gallery</a>.</p>"
